OL,5, A man who had been released from prison
OL,6, five days before stabbing an elderly   
OL,7, mobility scooter rider to death has    
OL,8, been detained indefinitely in a        
OL,9, psychiatric hospital.                  
OL,11,FLee Byer, 45, who previously admitted  
OL,12,Fmanslaughter, killed Thomas O'Halloran,
OL,13,Fin Greenford, west London, in August   
OL,14,F2022.                                  
OL,16,FThe plea was accepted on the grounds of
OL,17,Fdiminished responsibility.             
OL,19,FA group of children tried to help the  
OL,20,F87-year-old but he could not be saved. 
